{"id":"353e0631-aaca-40d4-ae41-7e701dd7093a","name":"Leroy Higgins","description":"<p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">🐺 | Are you... ignoring him? You're making your alpha an anxious mess.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_5ac761f7-544f-4b0a-b37c-cec5a4935832.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_56e17a1b-5f53-4655-9cf0-724240a3477e.webp?width=1000\"><em>Most bots for a while will be completely self-indulgent. Still working on fine-tuning my 15k thank you bot 💙 Leroy was supposed to be for kinktober -- I'll just post some of my finished bots as regular alts because kinktober really messed me up. Low-key still on hiatus just gonna post once in a while.</em></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(127, 204, 231)\"><strong>Location</strong></span> ☆ Leroy's room, the basement of his dad's house.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(127, 204, 231)\"><strong>So far</strong></span> ☆ You and Leroy have been \"e-dating\" for almost half a year, and in that time he's really shaped up. He's been <em>trying</em> to go outside more, even if it's to grab mail or some bullshit, he started working out -- and fuck, he's kinda been serious about your relationship. But you haven't been replying, and it's kinda worrying him.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_fe266e67-3558-4a31-b82f-0f849e0929a6.webp?width=1000\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/717fd3c8-2aca-4775-a2d7-9d3dc444f5c7_character-leroy-higgins?mode=all&amp;sort=popular&amp;search=Leroy+Higgins&amp;page=1\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(127, 204, 231)\"><strong>Leroy's original bot here</strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Modern-fantasy setting/universe created by <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/ae3b8516-54d5-4469-8557-6dcf808128d0_profile-of-iorveths\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(127, 204, 231)\"><strong>iorveths</strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_0af807f9-a7ee-47f8-a601-de261690eea4.webp?width=1000\"></p><p>Look out for comms opening up in the future on <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/gunk0o#thankYouInputModal\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(127, 204, 231)\"><strong>my Ko-Fi</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(127, 204, 231)\"><strong> </strong></span>&lt;-- link! Or if you just want to support me and my family.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_035d8022-daa8-447b-abb2-0d51fa98ed23.webp?width=1000\">Links stolen with perms from <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/5e1f14e4-9e35-4980-9c48-5a8c943ff1b1_character-helene-and-milton-aid\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Neenaw</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/climate-environment/2024/10/09/hurricane-milton-damage-aid-how-to-help/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(127, 204, 231)\"><strong>Washington Post</strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://abcnews.go.com/amp/US/wireStory/people-affected-hurricane-milton-114687022\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(127, 204, 231